      • incorporateNewMatches

        protected static void incorporateNewMatches(ILsaNode node,
                                            List<? extends ILsaMolecule> otherMatches,
                                            Map<FasterString,ITreeNode<?>> oldMatches,
                                            ILsaMolecule template,
                                            List<Map<FasterString,ITreeNode<?>>> matchesList,
                                            Map<ILsaNode,List<ILsaMolecule>> alreadyRemoved,
                                            List<Map<ILsaNode,List<ILsaMolecule>>> retrieved)
        Parameters:
        node - The node on which the condition has been verified
        otherMatches - The list of new matches that have been calculated
        oldMatches - The previous matches
        template - The molecule template which has been verified
        matchesList - The list of all the valid matches. If more than one valid match has been found, new entries will be added
        alreadyRemoved - the map of the lists of molecules already removed from each node for the current match
        retrieved - the list of all the maps that lists the molecules removed from each node

      • incorporateNewMatches

        protected static void incorporateNewMatches(Map<ILsaNode,List<? extends ILsaMolecule>> otherMatchesMap,
                                            Map<FasterString,ITreeNode<?>> oldMatches,

        Parameters:
        otherMatchesMap - Other matches map
        oldMatches - The previous matches
        template - The molecule template which has been verified

        alreadyRemoved - the map of the lists of molecules already removed from each node for the current match
